WEBVTT

00:01.044 --> 00:03.381
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>I am trying for Joy.</i>

00:03.381 --> 00:06.346
<i>She needs the real me.</i>

00:06.346 --> 00:07.682
OFFICER: These yours?

00:07.682 --> 00:09.853
<i>JOY: Have you</i>
<i>been taking your pills?</i>

00:09.853 --> 00:12.692
<i>ANNIE: Yes.</i>
<i>They gave them back to me.</i>

00:12.692 --> 00:14.863
<i>I've got these things</i>
<i>in my mind.</i>

00:14.863 --> 00:16.074
<i>[ominous music]</i>

00:16.074 --> 00:18.453
<i>People running around,</i>
<i>memories.</i>

00:18.453 --> 00:19.831
<i>I'm not right.</i>

00:19.831 --> 00:21.877
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:28.683 --> 00:31.104
<i>JAMAL: 400 years</i>
<i>she's been gathering speed,</i>

00:31.104 --> 00:32.524
heading for this place
at this time,

00:32.524 --> 00:33.901
and you think
you can stop her?

00:33.901 --> 00:36.532
<i>Tomorrow at dusk,</i>
<i>she returns.</i>

00:38.953 --> 00:40.582
‐ Go, go, go, go!
[train horn blares]

00:40.582 --> 00:42.669
‐ The train!
Move!

00:42.669 --> 00:44.965
[train siren blares]

00:44.965 --> 00:47.344
AUGUSTIN:
We'll give you a quiet end.

00:47.344 --> 00:49.390
Entombed in one of us.

00:49.390 --> 00:50.518
[gun clicks]

00:51.352 --> 00:53.566
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:58.283 --> 01:01.039
<i>NADIA: Pop?</i>

01:01.039 --> 01:03.669
<i>Can you talk, Pop?</i>

01:06.424 --> 01:08.094
<i>Come in, Pop!</i>

01:08.094 --> 01:10.600
[train horn blaring]

01:10.600 --> 01:13.606
<i>[disquieting music]</i>

01:13.606 --> 01:20.620
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:40.952 --> 01:43.958
[low moaning sounds]

01:43.958 --> 01:49.135
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:53.978 --> 01:55.690
[engine shuts off]

01:55.690 --> 02:02.704
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:24.956 --> 02:27.962
[bugs buzzing]

02:27.962 --> 02:34.976
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:44.746 --> 02:47.710
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

02:47.710 --> 02:54.724
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:10.756 --> 03:14.179
<i>AUGUSTIN:</i>
<i>Amity returns at sunset,</i>

03:14.179 --> 03:16.768
and this is our world now.

03:16.768 --> 03:18.814
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:18.814 --> 03:21.235
It is the world she gave us.

03:22.614 --> 03:24.534
That he gave us.

03:25.786 --> 03:28.917
<i>We waited 400 years.</i>

03:28.917 --> 03:31.673
<i>Now we know why.</i>

03:31.673 --> 03:33.761
<i>People have forgotten</i>

03:33.761 --> 03:37.184
<i>this land belongs</i>
<i>to the Angel.</i>

03:37.184 --> 03:40.315
<i>Now we take it back</i>
<i>in his name.</i>

03:40.315 --> 03:47.329
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:47.329 --> 03:49.751
<i>And when the prophet returns</i>
<i>to us tonight...</i>

03:49.751 --> 03:53.007
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:53.007 --> 03:56.515
<i>The real work will begin.</i>

03:56.515 --> 04:00.856
For first,
we must protect our new place

04:00.856 --> 04:06.450
<i>in this old, rotting world.</i>

04:06.450 --> 04:09.415
Then we will take
the rest of it

04:09.415 --> 04:12.254
from those who would oppose us.

04:12.254 --> 04:13.716
<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:13.716 --> 04:18.015
<i>The empty souls outside</i>
<i>these walls have a purpose.</i>

04:18.015 --> 04:19.936
<i>They will be her army.</i>

04:19.936 --> 04:22.608
<i>His army.</i>

04:22.608 --> 04:26.198
We will see this fight
through to the end.

04:26.198 --> 04:27.618
<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:27.618 --> 04:33.212
<i>The end of them is</i>
<i>the beginning of us.</i>

04:34.758 --> 04:40.811
<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:40.811 --> 04:43.817
<i>[ominous music]</i>

04:43.817 --> 04:50.330
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:10.075 --> 05:12.625
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>They all followed it</i>
<i>to the house,</i>

05:12.625 --> 05:14.419
<i>so if we get rid of it‐‐</i>

05:14.419 --> 05:16.257
ABDI: They'll snap out
of the fucking trance
they're in?

05:16.257 --> 05:17.927
