08:01.378 --> 08:04.342
<i>It's a door to other heres,</i>

08:04.342 --> 08:09.394
<i>other nows,</i>
<i>other dimensions.</i>

08:09.394 --> 08:11.398
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:11.398 --> 08:13.904
