25:26.592 --> 25:33.606
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25:51.349 --> 25:53.521
Little Love?

25:54.607 --> 25:56.736
Need anything?

25:58.322 --> 26:01.453
<i>♪ ♪</i>

26:01.453 --> 26:04.334
Do you want to talk about‐‐
‐ No.

26:04.334 --> 26:10.012
<i>♪ ♪</i>

26:20.825 --> 26:22.453
[gas pump clicks]

26:41.575 --> 26:44.581
<i>[disquieting music]</i>

26:44.581 --> 26:51.595
<i>♪ ♪</i>

27:16.394 --> 27:19.275
‐ Won't you just look
at this place?

27:21.362 --> 27:23.325
‐ What about Montreal?

27:23.325 --> 27:26.206
‐ Only an hour from here.

27:26.206 --> 27:28.460
And Joy,
the patient is bedridden,

27:28.460 --> 27:32.092
so it's basically
a whole house to ourselves.

27:32.092 --> 27:35.057
It's like Dunthorpe.

27:37.102 --> 27:40.067
Almost like a storybook house.

27:45.077 --> 27:47.582
<i>INTERVIEWER: Looks like</i>
<i>you've worked all over.</i>

27:47.582 --> 27:49.460
Where are you from originally?

27:49.460 --> 27:52.509
‐ Nowhere, really.
Military brat.

27:52.509 --> 27:54.303
My father,
that good old guy,

27:54.303 --> 27:58.061
God rest his soul‐‐
he moved us around a lot.

27:59.815 --> 28:01.359
INTERVIEWER:
Is this okay?

28:01.359 --> 28:03.238
‐ Perfect.
Thank you.

28:03.238 --> 28:05.660
‐ Take any room you like,
dear.

28:06.829 --> 28:08.666
‐ Oh, take the room next
to mine, Little Love.

28:14.010 --> 28:15.763
‐ The hormones hit.

28:15.763 --> 28:18.644
It's like a stranger's living
in your house, eh?

28:18.644 --> 28:20.857
[door closes]

28:20.857 --> 28:23.069
<i>ANNIE: "Gregory</i>
<i>had come back from the Crimea</i>

28:23.069 --> 28:24.865
<i>"a different man.</i>

28:24.865 --> 28:27.036
"It wasn't just
the soldier's beard

28:27.036 --> 28:30.375
"or the crosshatched scar
on his left forearm.

28:30.375 --> 28:32.421
"It was his eyes.

28:32.421 --> 28:35.344
"They didn't look out
at Misery anymore.

28:35.344 --> 28:39.936
"They looked in at something
only he could see,

28:39.936 --> 28:43.694
something war and time
had written on‐‐"

28:43.694 --> 28:45.531
‐ [groans]

28:45.531 --> 28:52.545
<i>♪ ♪</i>

29:00.018 --> 29:02.565
[breathing machine hisses]

29:22.856 --> 29:25.277
‐ Beautiful, isn't it?

29:27.406 --> 29:30.120
I really think
this could be it, Joy.

29:31.080 --> 29:32.667
The Laughing Place.

29:36.633 --> 29:38.721
[sighs]

29:40.015 --> 29:42.060
I was thinking next time
I go into town,

29:42.060 --> 29:44.106
I can get you some hair dye.

29:44.106 --> 29:45.777
Get it back to normal.

29:45.777 --> 29:47.279
‐ I like it this way.

29:58.803 --> 30:01.809
<i>[ominous music]</i>

30:01.809 --> 30:08.823
<i>♪ ♪</i>

30:17.047 --> 30:21.305
<i>[actor speaking French]</i>

30:48.569 --> 30:51.658
<i>[actor sobs,</i>
<i>continues speaking French]</i>

31:02.346 --> 31:04.141
‐ That's enough of that.

31:26.603 --> 31:29.651
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

31:29.651 --> 31:36.665
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:46.643 --> 31:48.312
[phone beeps]

31:48.981 --> 31:50.568
<i>MYSTERIOUS PERSON:</i>
<i>Tomorrow then.</i>

31:50.568 --> 31:52.446
<i>I'll be waiting.</i>

31:52.446 --> 31:54.408
<i>JOY:</i>
<i>Tomorrow.</i>

31:54.408 --> 32:01.380
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:09.021 --> 32:11.108
[knock on door]

32:11.108 --> 32:13.947
‐ Joy?
‐ Yeah?

32:16.578 --> 32:18.498
‐ Who were you talking to?

32:18.498 --> 32:19.542
‐ What?
ANNIE: On the phone.

32:19.542 --> 32:21.420
You were talking to someone.

32:21.420 --> 32:23.926
‐ Uh, I wasn't on the phone.

32:23.926 --> 32:26.807
‐ Was it...
‐ What?

32:26.807 --> 32:28.977
‐ Someone from back there?

32:30.146 --> 32:32.652
‐ Are you feeling okay?

32:32.652 --> 32:35.783
Are you running low
on pills again?

32:35.783 --> 32:38.329
‐ This isn't about me.
Who‐‐who were you talking to?

32:38.329 --> 32:40.668
‐ I wasn't on the phone.

32:40.668 --> 32:43.172
What do you want me to say?

32:45.845 --> 32:47.305
‐ [sighs]

32:47.305 --> 32:50.103
<i>[somber music]</i>

32:50.103 --> 32:57.117
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:05.634 --> 33:07.680
<i>VOICE: Annie...</i>

33:09.349 --> 33:16.363
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:33.481 --> 33:38.617
<i>That filth</i>
<i>will never come out.</i>

33:40.328 --> 33:43.209
<i>You make her clean.</i>

33:44.169 --> 33:46.423
[washing machine rattles]

33:53.145 --> 33:55.024
‐ I need to ask you something.

33:55.024 --> 33:56.945
‐ I told you,
I wasn't on the phone.

33:56.945 --> 33:58.615
‐ No.

33:59.701 --> 34:01.161
You said that you don't want
to talk

34:01.161 --> 34:03.542
about what happened
at that house,

34:03.542 --> 34:05.169
but I need to know, Joy.

34:05.169 --> 34:07.048
What they did to you,
those people,

34:07.048 --> 34:10.221
that...man,

34:10.221 --> 34:12.058
before we got there.

34:13.394 --> 34:15.481
‐ I don't know.

34:15.481 --> 34:16.776
‐ What do you mean?

34:18.279 --> 34:20.241
‐ I don't remember.

34:20.241 --> 34:23.623
‐ You don't remember?
‐ No.

34:23.623 --> 34:25.460
‐ Joy‐‐
‐ What?

34:25.460 --> 34:27.464
[sighs]

34:39.154 --> 34:42.160
[shower running]

34:47.880 --> 34:50.844
<i>[ominous music]</i>

34:50.844 --> 34:57.858
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:24.411 --> 35:27.041
‐ [whimpering] My Joy...

35:27.041 --> 35:34.014
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:03.782 --> 36:06.788
<i>[ominous music]</i>

36:06.788 --> 36:13.760
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:40.479 --> 36:42.651
‐ Thought you might want some.

36:43.570 --> 36:44.947
‐ I'm all right.

36:44.947 --> 36:47.493
‐ Since when do you
not like ice cream?

36:48.747 --> 36:50.751
Since when does anyone?

36:50.751 --> 36:53.088
‐ Okay.

36:53.088 --> 37:00.061
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:24.860 --> 37:26.154
‐ Do you like it?

37:28.450 --> 37:30.664
‐ It tastes weird.

37:30.664 --> 37:33.670
<i>[disquieting music]</i>

37:33.670 --> 37:37.636
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:37.636 --> 37:39.682
Is there some‐‐

37:39.682 --> 37:42.061
did you put something in that?

37:42.061 --> 37:43.230
‐ Medicine.

37:44.441 --> 37:46.696
‐ What medicine?
‐ Haldol.

37:46.696 --> 37:48.240
‐ What the fuck?

37:48.240 --> 37:50.704
‐ Such dirty words,

37:50.704 --> 37:52.583
not like my Joy.

37:52.583 --> 37:55.379
‐ You drugged me?
You're crazy!

37:55.379 --> 37:57.383
‐ You didn't think I'd know?

37:57.383 --> 38:00.724
My own girl,
my own sweet girl,

38:00.724 --> 38:03.145
and you didn't think I'd know
that you were one of them?

38:03.145 --> 38:04.732
‐ You're the one
who needs medicine!

38:04.732 --> 38:06.318
You're the monster!
‐ Shut your mouth!

38:06.318 --> 38:07.946
‐ Mom, no!

38:07.946 --> 38:09.992
‐ But I'm not your mom, am I?

38:09.992 --> 38:12.330
‐ Mom, stop, stop!
Help!

38:12.330 --> 38:13.917
Stop it!

38:13.917 --> 38:15.796
‐ Guess you need a bigger dose!
‐ [muffled grunt]

38:19.512 --> 38:20.972
‐ [yells]

38:23.310 --> 38:25.314
‐ [pants]

38:25.314 --> 38:32.245
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:38.173 --> 38:40.052
‐ Come back here!

38:43.768 --> 38:45.772
You think you could
just take my Joy?

38:45.772 --> 38:48.026
‐ Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!

38:50.281 --> 38:53.328
[both panting]

38:55.124 --> 38:57.003
‐ [screams]

39:08.610 --> 39:10.279
[gasps]

39:20.174 --> 39:23.640
‐ [pants]

39:43.805 --> 39:46.811
<i>[somber music]</i>

39:46.811 --> 39:53.825
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:13.405 --> 40:16.328
[panting]

41:06.094 --> 41:08.641
<i>JOY:</i>
<i>Mom, I'm sorry.</i>

41:08.641 --> 41:12.148
<i>I hope this isn't forever,</i>
<i>but right now,</i>

41:12.148 --> 41:13.734
<i>I have to go.</i>

41:13.734 --> 41:17.074
<i>I know you won't understand.</i>
<i>I hope you don't hate me.</i>

41:17.074 --> 41:18.995
<i>I don't want you to hate me.</i>

41:18.995 --> 41:21.332
<i>I just need to be someone else</i>
<i>for a while,</i>

41:21.332 --> 41:25.257
<i>because I don't know how to be</i>
<i>your little girl anymore.</i>

41:25.257 --> 41:27.971
<i>It's not about what happened</i>
<i>in Maine.</i>

41:27.971 --> 41:31.019
<i>I don't remember a lot</i>
<i>of that, to be honest.</i>

41:31.019 --> 41:33.398
<i>I'm actually working</i>
<i>on forgetting it.</i>

41:33.398 --> 41:37.072
<i>The truth is, what happened</i>
<i>to us happened before Maine,</i>

41:37.072 --> 41:38.659
<i>before Rita.</i>

41:38.659 --> 41:40.580
<i>Maybe I don't know</i>
<i>who I am yet,</i>

41:40.580 --> 41:44.086
<i>but I know I can't</i>
<i>figure it out with you.</i>

41:44.086 --> 41:47.384
<i>I lied about the phone.</i>
<i>I had to.</i>

41:47.384 --> 41:49.180
<i>I didn't want to make you</i>
<i>feel crazy,</i>

41:49.180 --> 41:52.102
<i>but I had to talk to a lawyer</i>
<i>about getting emancipated,</i>

41:52.102 --> 41:54.398
<i>how to make it all legal,</i>
<i>like Chance did.</i>

41:54.398 --> 41:56.110
<i>[frantic orchestral music]</i>

41:56.110 --> 41:58.699
<i>Please don't try to find me.</i>

41:58.699 --> 42:02.331
<i>I'll find you someday,</i>
<i>I promise.</i>

42:02.331 --> 42:03.543
<i>When I'm ready.</i>

42:03.543 --> 42:09.387
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:09.387 --> 42:11.432
‐ Joy!

42:11.432 --> 42:14.606
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:14.606 --> 42:16.484
Joy!
Joy!

42:16.484 --> 42:18.656
[pants]

42:18.656 --> 42:20.284
Joy!

42:20.284 --> 42:21.579
[pants]

42:22.581 --> 42:24.458
[breathes]

42:26.922 --> 42:28.049
Joy.

42:28.968 --> 42:31.180
[sobs]

42:32.559 --> 42:34.145
Please!

42:34.145 --> 42:36.692
I would never hurt you.
Please...

42:36.692 --> 42:39.363
[pants heavily]

42:41.200 --> 42:43.914
Joy.
Joy!

42:46.044 --> 42:48.507
Come back, Joy.

42:49.968 --> 42:52.849
Please, come back.

42:52.849 --> 42:54.936
Please!

42:56.439 --> 42:58.778
‐ [coughing, sputtering]

42:58.778 --> 43:00.948
‐ Joy!
Joy!

43:00.948 --> 43:03.161
Oh, little‐‐
my Little Love.

43:03.161 --> 43:05.374
[both sob]

43:05.374 --> 43:07.294
‐ Mom.

43:07.294 --> 43:09.966
Mom.

43:09.966 --> 43:12.346
What...
[coughs]

43:12.346 --> 43:14.643
What‐‐what happened?

43:14.643 --> 43:16.479
What happened?

43:17.816 --> 43:20.112
‐ You fell in the water.

43:21.364 --> 43:23.828
You fell in the water.
You almost drowned.

43:24.830 --> 43:26.207
‐ [coughs]

43:26.207 --> 43:28.128
You‐‐you saved me.

43:28.128 --> 43:31.342
[both sob]

43:37.271 --> 43:38.524
RUFUS WAINWRIGHT:
♪ Coming through the fog ♪

43:38.524 --> 43:42.114
♪ Your sons and daughters ♪

43:42.114 --> 43:45.328
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:45.328 --> 43:49.378
♪ Let the river run ♪

43:49.378 --> 43:52.677
♪ Let all the dreamers ♪

43:52.677 --> 43:55.808
♪ Wake the nation ♪

43:55.808 --> 44:02.739
♪ Come, the New Jerusalem ♪

44:03.323 --> 44:07.665
♪ Silver cities rise ♪

44:07.665 --> 44:10.212
♪ The morning lights ♪

44:10.212 --> 44:13.594
♪ The streets that meet them ♪

44:13.594 --> 44:16.349
♪ And sirens call them on ♪

44:16.349 --> 44:18.604
‐ One for one, Little Love?
‐ Okay.

44:21.777 --> 44:23.238
‐ Hey!

44:23.238 --> 44:27.454
RUFUS WAINWRIGHT:
♪ It's asking for the taking ♪

44:27.454 --> 44:29.918
[laughter]

44:29.918 --> 44:33.299
♪ Trembling, shaking ♪

44:33.299 --> 44:38.769
♪ Oh, my heart is aching ♪

44:38.769 --> 44:40.982
‐ Hey, I call shotgun.

44:40.982 --> 44:42.610
RUFUS WAINWRIGHT:
♪ Coming through the fog ♪

44:42.610 --> 44:44.196
♪ Your sons and daughters ♪

44:44.196 --> 44:47.996
♪ We the great and small ♪

44:47.996 --> 44:50.751
♪ Stand on a star ♪

44:50.751 --> 44:55.343
♪ And blaze a trail of desire ♪

44:56.513 --> 45:00.855
♪ Through the darkening dawn ♪

45:04.445 --> 45:06.658
‐ Can you believe
we're really here?

45:06.658 --> 45:09.413
‐ I'm so excited.

45:09.413 --> 45:12.419
<i>[gentle music]</i>

45:12.419 --> 45:18.097
<i>♪ ♪</i>

45:19.684 --> 45:21.479
‐ Would you look at
all these people?

45:21.479 --> 45:27.575
<i>♪ ♪</i>

45:27.575 --> 45:29.161
‐ Are we gonna get to meet him?

45:29.161 --> 45:30.455
‐ I hope so.

45:30.455 --> 45:32.710
He's very busy
with all of his readings.

45:32.710 --> 45:35.716
<i>♪ ♪</i>

45:41.770 --> 45:43.732
‐ Do you think I could draw
the covers for him one day?

45:43.732 --> 45:45.360
‐ Of course I do.

45:45.360 --> 45:46.947
‐ You really think
I'm good enough?

45:46.947 --> 45:49.995
‐ Joy, I think you're the best
artist in the whole world.

45:51.247 --> 45:53.209
FAN:
Is this seat taken?

45:54.921 --> 45:56.925
‐ Of course it is, Mister!

46:01.810 --> 46:03.856
Sorry about that,
Little Love.

46:03.856 --> 46:05.693
‐ It's okay, Mom.

46:05.693 --> 46:07.947
I'm just happy we're here
together.

46:09.033 --> 46:10.661
‐ Me too.

46:10.661 --> 46:12.456
‐ [gasps]
Look!

46:12.456 --> 46:19.344
<i>♪ ♪</i>

46:19.344 --> 46:22.643
Oh, we have to get him
to dedicate a book to you.

46:22.643 --> 46:27.194
<i>♪ ♪</i>

46:27.194 --> 46:29.156
‐ Of course he will.

46:30.659 --> 46:32.663
I'm his number one fan.

46:32.663 --> 46:35.669
<i>[ominous music]</i>

46:35.669 --> 46:42.642
<i>♪ ♪</i>

48:13.573 --> 48:15.410
<i>CHILD:</i>
<i>Bad Robot!</i>

48:15.410 --> 48:18.416
[sharp click]

48:18.416 --> 48:21.422
<i>[fanfare]</i>

48:21.422 --> 48:23.301
<i>[jingle]</i>
